l:dependency.name: Coverage Plugin
l:dependency.l:description: Collects reports of code coverage or mutation coverage tools and visualizes the results. It has support for the following report formats: JaCoCo, Cobertura, and PIT.

l:dependency.name: Byte Buddy (without dependencies)
l:dependency.l:description: Byte Buddy is a Java library for creating Java classes at run time. This artifact is a build of Byte Buddy with all ASM dependencies repackaged into its own name space.

l:dependency.name: Caffeine API Plugin
l:dependency.l:description: Jenkins plugin that packages Caffeine for use by other plugins.

l:dependency.name: Code Coverage Model and Parsers
l:dependency.l:description: Provides a Java API and model to parse and collect code coverage results
